1. On nema *alibi* za svoje postupke. (He has no *alibi* for his actions.) 
2. Advokat je izneo snažan *alibi* za svog klijenta. (The lawyer presented a strong *alibi* for his client.)
3. Policija još uvek traži *alibi* osumnjičenog. (The police are still searching for the suspect's *alibi*.)
4. Sudija je odbacio njegov *alibi* kao neistinit. (The judge dismissed his *alibi* as untrue.)
5. Njegov *alibi* se pokazao lažnim. (His *alibi* proved to be false.)
6. Moramo pronaći *alibi* za naše odsustvo. (We need to find an *alibi* for our absence.)
7. Sumnjam da ima *alibi* za svoje kašnjenje. (I doubt he has an *alibi* for his tardiness.)
8. Postoje indicije da će njegov *alibi* biti osporen. (There are indications that his *alibi* will be challenged.)